99f40b59-918d-462e-8d17-cea0dca8a3de.title: Note
99f40b59-918d-462e-8d17-cea0dca8a3de.text: Did you talk to Ted or Martha?

b0f89c48-634d-4fac-a007-f01c7dd8367e.title: <player>
b0f89c48-634d-4fac-a007-f01c7dd8367e.text:
Hello. Your parents say you saw what happened to
Elena...

85dbdc06-9646-451c-9a71-49da36b3003a.title: Milli Rehnison
85dbdc06-9646-451c-9a71-49da36b3003a.text:
*sniff* Yes I was near the south east corner when I
saw Elena walking by. I was about to run to greet her
when some men jumped out. They shoved a sack over
her head and dragged her into a building.

7150eb45-1e31-49c0-86bb-7139f7551a3b.title: Milli Rehnison
7150eb45-1e31-49c0-86bb-7139f7551a3b.text:
It was the boarded up building with no windows in the
south east corner of West Ardougne.

e937dcb9-f973-4aa3-8361-8d29782a785e.title: Milli Rehnison
e937dcb9-f973-4aa3-8361-8d29782a785e.text: I hope you find her. She was nice.

033a3510-abd0-4a69-bd0a-851fb4366680.title: Milli Rehnison
033a3510-abd0-4a69-bd0a-851fb4366680.text: I hope she comes and visits sometime.
